metadata.name: Bug-eyed Meditations #1
metadata.description:
He couldn’t be still. After years of practicing, he still couldn’t just sit still. 

The thoughts shuddered through his body rattling his mind, still pondering how we got here - raging wars, economic meltdowns, and putting our hopes in the almighty coin.. that coin. Only if! 

Anneatta broke his meditation with a scream from the now empty kitchen, “Whos gonna feed the baby Deanon!!”.

P.S. Art inspo punk6529
